                        <li>Explore the vibrant Leh market.</li>
                        <li>Overnight stay in Leh.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Day 3: Leh to Nubra Valley (via Khardung La)</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Drive through the world’s highest motorable pass, Khardung La.</li>
                        <li>Visit Diskit Monastery and the famous Maitreya Buddha statue.</li>
                        <li>Enjoy a camel ride in the Hunder sand dunes.</li>
                        <li>Overnight stay in Nubra Valley.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Day 4: Nubra Valley to Pangong Lake</strong>
