                        <li>Early morning drive back to Leh.</li>
                        <li>Visit the Hemis Monastery en route.</li>
                        <li>Evening at leisure in Leh.</li>
                        <li>Overnight stay in Leh.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Day 6: Leh to Lamayuru (via Magnetic Hill and Alchi Monastery)</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Visit the mystical Magnetic Hill, Sangam (confluence of Zanskar and Indus rivers), and Alchi Monastery.</li>
                        <li>Continue to Lamayuru Monastery, known for its moon-like landscapes.</li>
                        <li>Return to Leh for an overnight stay.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
